{"name": "odoo13-addon-sale-manual-delivery", "metadata": {"name": "odoo13-addon-sale-manual-delivery", "version": "13.0.1.2.0", "classifiers": ["Framework :: Odoo", "Framework :: Odoo :: 13.0", "License :: OSI Approved :: GNU Affero General Public License v3", "Programming Language :: Python"], "home_page": "https://github.com/OCA/sale-workflow", "license": "AGPL-3", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["odoo"], "summary": "Create manually your deliveries", "upload_time": 1733500694}, "documentation": ["---\nsubstitutions:\n  badge1: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/maturity-Beta-yellow.png\n    :alt: Beta\n    :target: https://odoo-community.org/page/development-status\n    ```\n  badge2: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/licence-AGPL--3-blue.png\n    :alt: 'License: AGPL-3'\n    :target: http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0-standalone.html\n    ```\n  badge3: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/github-OCA%2Fsale--workflow-lightgray.png?logo=github\n    :alt: OCA/sale-workflow\n    :target: https://github.com/OCA/sale-workflow/tree/13.0/sale_manual_delivery\n    ```\n  badge4: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/weblate-Translate%20me-F47D42.png\n    :alt: Translate me on Weblate\n    :target: https://translation.odoo-community.org/projects/sale-workflow-13-0/sale-workflow-13-0-sale_manual_delivery\n    ```\n  badge5: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/runboat-Try%20me-875A7B.png\n    :alt: Try me on Runboat\n    :target: https://runboat.odoo-community.org/builds?repo=OCA/sale-workflow&target_branch=13.0\n    ```\n---\n\n# Sale Manual Delivery\n\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! This file is generated by oca-gen-addon-readme !!\n% !! changes will be overwritten.                   !!\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! source digest: sha256:d25cb0a51ac9501894ca28df3fc50ac5fa722abc311aacd0373bf99ea3b42fd2\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n\n{{ badge1 }} {{ badge2 }} {{ badge3 }} {{ badge4 }} {{ badge5 }}\n\nThe goal of this module is to allow the manual creation of delivery slips. If activated,\na sale order won't directly impact the stock. It will not make a reservation on the stock.\nIt allows the delivery and the impact on stock to be done manually when needed.\nThe goal is to be used on long term projects where not all the material is shipped at once.\nAs you make many shipments, every time you make a new delivery, you can choose an new carrier as well\nas a planned date. A wizard helps you to chose what to deliver by showing you how much you already\nplanned to ship.\n\n**Table of contents**\n\n```{contents}\n:local: true\n```\n\n## Known issues / Roadmap\n\n- Add Screenshots\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/OCA/sale-workflow/issues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us to smash it by providing a detailed and welcomed\n[feedback](https://github.com/OCA/sale-workflow/issues/new?body=module:%20sale_manual_delivery%0Aversion:%2013.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- Camptocamp SA\n\n### Contributors\n\n- Denis Leemann \\<<mailto:denis.leemann@camptocamp.com>>\n- Joel Grand-Guillaume \\<<mailto:joel.grandguillaume@camptocamp.com>>\n- Phuc Tran Thanh \\<<mailto:phuc@trobz.com>>\n- Iv\u00e1n Todorovich \\<<mailto:ivan.todorovich@gmail.com>>\n\n### Maintainers\n\nThis module is maintained by the OCA.\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/logo.png\n:alt: Odoo Community Association\n:target: https://odoo-community.org\n```\n\nOCA, or the Odoo Community Association, is a nonprofit organization whose\nmission is to support the collaborative development of Odoo features and\npromote its widespread use.\n\nThis module is part of the [OCA/sale-workflow](https://github.com/OCA/sale-workflow/tree/13.0/sale_manual_delivery) project on GitHub.\n\nYou are welcome to contribute. To learn how please visit <https://odoo-community.org/page/Contribute>.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.sale_manual_delivery.wizard", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.sale_manual_delivery.wizard.manual_delivery", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.sale_manual_delivery.wizard..manual_delivery", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.sale_manual_delivery.wizard.manual_delivery_line", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.sale_manual_delivery.wizard..manual_delivery_line", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "odoo.addons.sale_manual_delivery.models.procurement_group", "documentation": ["Copyright 2017 Denis Leemann, Camptocamp SA", "Copyright 2021 Iv\u00e1n Todorovich, Camptocamp SA", "License AGPL-3.0 or later (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl.html)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "odoo.addons.sale_manual_delivery.models.procurement_group.ProcurementGroup", "bases": ["models.Model"], "methods": [], "class_variables": [{"name": "odoo.addons.sale_manual_delivery.models.procurement_group.ProcurementGroup._inherit", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.sale_manual_delivery.models.procurement_group.ProcurementGroup.date_planned", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": []}], "exports": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.sale_manual_delivery.models", "documentation": ["License AGPL-3.0 or later (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.sale_manual_delivery.models.crm_team", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.sale_manual_delivery.models..crm_team", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.sale_manual_delivery.models.procurement_group", "xref": {"